{
  "stem": "935.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a prisoner, also a lesbian, who was a [INAUDIBLE] [? arbiter, ?] or what you say, you know, in charge of the column, watched me and said to me, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What did you do on the outside?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like this is the only job in the world, digging potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after three weeks, she demoted me, and I went back into the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As little as possible, I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I I just know I started singing again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not for the Nazis anymore, but for the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And had a very good friend there, made a very good friend, who was also one of the 80 who was with me, shipped from Auschwitz to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eva.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She collected the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, a bit of toilet paper, a bit of soap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what happened to your, your-- the typhus?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How did you recover?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never had typhus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the sores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These here healed, but the one on my foot didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I treated them, or I'd say, Eva treated them with dirty machine rags.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, the hospital there-- there was a hospital too, but it was also one you're better off not going into.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The doctor there, he was into injections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody knew what was into the injections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody knew what was into the injections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Except that you were very wise not to get close to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You came out minus a lot of things which you needed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you-- you didn't go near a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In these two years, except for just at the end-- this was very dangerous already, because it was very, very deep, and very painful.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
